request.description:
Returns the health status of the application including PostgreSQL and Redis. Both must show UP before proceeding.

Expected response:  
{  
"status": "UP",  
"components": {  
"db": { "status": "UP" },  
"redis": { "status": "UP" }  
}  
}

Returns the total impression count and a variant breakdown for the last 7 days for the boolean flag.

Expected response:
{
  "flagKey": "checkout-redesign",
  "totalImpressions": 5,
  "last7Days": [
    { "variant": null, "count": 5 }
  ]
}

Returns impression stats for the A/B flag with a breakdown by variant. The last7Days array shows how many users received each variant.

Expected response:
{
  "flagKey": "homepage-ab-test",
  "totalImpressions": 5,
  "last7Days": [
    { "variant": "control",   "count": 3 },
    { "variant": "treatment", "count": 2 }
  ]
}
